---------------------------------------------------

This is the second release after fixing invalid spawn points
and adding a new skybox.  Also added two more spawn
points for a total of 34 spawn points.
Also included a nav file.

---------------------------------------------------

This is a map I created for my gg server.

Note: Nothing fancy here.  No arches, rounded corners
or anything that would hinder fps.  This map was built
as simple as possible to promote a high quality of
gameplay but yet tried to give the map an appealing
side also.
Strategically placed crates and designed for close quarters
gameplay and also a few sniping spots.

I did a test run on my server and players really liked the
way they were able to maneuver smoothly and freely from
one area to another.  Makes for a fun round of fragging.  

----------------------------------------------------

Open to all constructive criticism.
